sequenceDiagram
    actor O as Operator
    participant B as Browser
    participant API as POST /api/customers
    participant V as Zod Validator
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Q as BullMQ (Redis)
    participant W as MikroTik Worker
    participant MT as MikroTik RouterOS

    O->>B: Submit form pelanggan
    B->>API: POST { name, packageId, pppoeUsername, ... }
    API->>V: createCustomerSchema.parse()
    V-->>API: data terverifikasi
    API->>DB: INSERT INTO customers (...)
    DB-->>API: customer { id, customerId }
    API->>Q: enqueueCreatePPPoE({ username, password, profile })
    Q-->>API: jobId
    API-->>B: 201 Created { customer, jobId }
    B-->>O: Toast "Pelanggan ditambahkan"

    Q->>W: deliver job CREATE_PPPOE
    W->>MT: /ppp/secret/add name=... password=... profile=...
    MT-->>W: ok
    W->>Q: ack (job complete)

    opt Pemeriksaan status job
        B->>API: GET /api/jobs/{jobId}
        API->>Q: getJob(jobId)
        Q-->>API: { state: completed }
        API-->>B: { status: "completed" }
    end
